bugfinder.midRiskBugText:
Bugs can affect the security of the target system but cannot be directly proved to be available;
Bugs able to obtain target network device permissions but determined not to be further utilized;
Non-critical information leakage, open URL jump bugs, XSS bugs with certain restrictions and difficult to be utilized, CSRF bugs of non-core key business operations, etc.
High-risk bugs require specific addresses to be triggered, such as the numerical overflow bugs that can be triggered by the holder of the token contract; Access control defects of non-critical functions and logic design defects that cannot cause direct capital loss.

stpes.intro:
The ERC20 token based on ethereum TRUE will switch to the TrueChain mainnet coin; 
TRUE wallet will launch a number of new applications;
TRUE will enter a number of new international trading platforms;
TRUE will emerge in applications of assets circulation.

a number of offline road shows and publicity activities will be carried out in Europe, East Asia, Southeast Asia and North America.
TrueChain will appear in the 2019 Malta AI & Blockchain Summit;
A number of high-quality assets will be selected to launch through Pandaq platform.
